## 2. UI KIT BUILDER EVALUATION

### 2.1 UI Kit Builder Access

#### Issue 2.1.1: Builder Link Hard to Find
**Severity:** High  
**Expected:** Prominent "Build UI Kit" button on dashboard  
**Actual:** Buried in "Integrations" submenu  
**Impact:** Users miss this key feature  
**Suggestion:** Add featured card on dashboard home page

#### Issue 2.1.2: No Explanation of What UI Kit Builder Does
**Severity:** Medium  
**Expected:** Brief description or video showing what builder generates  
**Actual:** Just a button with no context  
**Impact:** Users unsure if they need it  
**Suggestion:** Add tooltip: "Generate pre-built chat components for your platform"

### 2.2 Configuration Process

#### Issue 2.2.1: Theme Preview Not Updating Live
**Severity:** Critical  
**Expected:** Preview updates in real-time as colors/fonts changed  
**Actual:** Preview remains static until page refresh  
**Impact:** Must reload multiple times to see changes  
**Suggestion:** Implement live preview with debounced state updates

#### Issue 2.2.2: Color Picker Lacks Preset Themes
**Severity:** Medium  
**Expected:** Popular theme presets (Dark, Light, Blue, etc.)  
**Actual:** Must manually configure all colors  
**Impact:** Time-consuming for users wanting standard themes  
**Suggestion:** Add 5-6 preset themes with one-click apply

#### Issue 2.2.3: Font Selection Limited
**Severity:** Low  
**Expected:** Google Fonts integration with search  
**Actual:** Only 5 system fonts available  
**Impact:** Limited customization  
**Suggestion:** Integrate Google Fonts API

### 2.3 Component Selection

#### Issue 2.3.1: Component Descriptions Missing
**Severity:** High  
**Expected:** Each component has description and preview  
**Actual:** Just component names with checkboxes  
**Impact:** Users don't know what "ConversationsWithMessages" includes  
**Suggestion:** Add expandable descriptions with screenshots

#### Issue 2.3.2: No "Select All" Option
**Severity:** Low  
**Expected:** Quick select all/none toggles  
**Actual:** Must check each component individually  
**Impact:** Tedious for users wanting full kit  
**Suggestion:** Add "Select All" and "Select None" buttons

#### Issue 2.3.3: Dependencies Not Indicated
**Severity:** Medium  
**Expected:** Show if selecting Component A requires Component B  
**Actual:** No dependency information  
**Impact:** Generated kit may have missing dependencies  
**Suggestion:** Add dependency indicators and auto-select required components

### 2.4 Download Process

#### Issue 2.4.1: Download Button Stays Disabled
**Severity:** Critical  
**Expected:** Button enables after all required fields filled  
**Actual:** Button remains disabled even with valid configuration  
**Impact:** Cannot download generated kit  
**Suggestion:** Debug validation logic, add console logging to identify blocking field

#### Issue 2.4.2: No Progress Indicator During Generation
**Severity:** Medium  
**Expected:** Progress bar showing "Generating kit... 60%"  
**Actual:** Blank screen for 15-20 seconds  
**Impact:** Users think page crashed  
**Suggestion:** Add progress indicator with estimated time

#### Issue 2.4.3: Downloaded File Name Not Descriptive
**Severity:** Low  
**Expected:** "cometchat-uikit-react-dark-theme-v1.zip"  
**Actual:** "download.zip"  
**Impact:** Hard to organize multiple downloads  
**Suggestion:** Generate descriptive filename with platform, theme, date

### 2.5 Generated Code Quality

#### Issue 2.5.1: Generated Code Has Linting Errors
**Severity:** Medium  
**Expected:** Clean code passing ESLint standard rules  
**Actual:** 23 linting errors in generated components  
**Impact:** Warnings flood console, unprofessional  
**Suggestion:** Run ESLint on generated code before packaging

#### Issue 2.5.2: Unused Imports in Generated Files
**Severity:** Low  
**Expected:** Only used imports included  
**Actual:** Many unused imports increase bundle size  
**Impact:** Larger build size  
**Suggestion:** Use AST analysis to remove unused imports

