## 3. DOCUMENTATION EVALUATION

### 3.1 Getting Started Guide

#### Issue 3.1.1: Installation Command Uses Old Package Name
**Severity:** Critical  
**Expected:** `npm install @cometchat/chat-uikit-react`  
**Actual:** Documentation shows `@cometchat-pro/react-ui-kit` (deprecated)  
**Impact:** Installation fails with 404 error  
**Suggestion:** Update all documentation to current package names

#### Issue 3.1.2: Prerequisites Not Listed
**Severity:** High  
**Expected:** Clear list: "Node 16+, npm 8+, React 17+"  
**Actual:** No system requirements mentioned  
**Impact:** Users with Node 14 get cryptic errors  
**Suggestion:** Add "Prerequisites" section at top of guide

#### Issue 3.1.3: No Quick Start Template
**Severity:** Medium  
**Expected:** `npx create-cometchat-app my-app` scaffold command  
**Actual:** Must manually set up project structure  
**Impact:** Slow onboarding  
**Suggestion:** Create CLI tool or provide GitHub template repository

### 3.2 API Reference

#### Issue 3.2.1: Code Examples Have Syntax Errors
**Severity:** High  
**Expected:** Copy-pasteable working code  
**Actual:** Examples have missing brackets, undefined variables  
**Impact:** Code fails when copied directly  
**Suggestion:** Test all code examples in actual project

#### Issue 3.2.2: Return Types Not Documented
**Severity:** Medium  
**Expected:** Each method shows return type and shape  
**Actual:** Only input parameters documented  
**Impact:** Users must console.log to discover response structure  
**Suggestion:** Add TypeScript-style return type annotations

#### Issue 3.2.3: Error Codes Not Listed
**Severity:** Medium  
**Expected:** Table of error codes with descriptions  
**Actual:** Errors mentioned but codes not documented  
**Impact:** Cannot programmatically handle specific errors  
**Suggestion:** Create error code reference page

### 3.3 Integration Guides

#### Issue 3.3.1: React Guide Missing Environment Variables
**Severity:** High  
**Expected:** Complete .env file template  
**Actual:** Only APP_ID shown, AUTH_KEY location unclear  
**Impact:** App fails to initialize  
