## 6. POSITIVE ASPECTS

Despite the issues found, several aspects of the platform work well:

1. **Intuitive Core Concept**: The idea of a visual UI Kit Builder is excellent
2. **Comprehensive Components**: Wide range of chat components available
3. **Good API Design**: Core SDK methods are well-structured
4. **Active Development**: Regular updates visible in changelog
5. **Multiple Platform Support**: React, React Native, iOS, Android, Flutter coverage

