## 7. CONCLUSION

The CometChat platform has strong potential but suffers from polish issues that impact the developer experience. The most critical issues are around the UI Kit Builder download functionality and documentation accuracy. Addressing the Priority 1 items would significantly improve the onboarding experience for new developers.

